  "prompt": "How can I know about the luxury hotel in Bhopal?",
  "response": "To find information about luxury hotels in Bhopal, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Online Search:**\n   - Use search engines like Google and type keywords such as \"luxury hotels in Bhopal\" or \"best luxury hotels Bhopal.\"\n   - Visit travel websites like Booking.com, TripAdvisor, or Expedia. These platforms often have detailed listings, customer reviews, and ratings that can help you make an informed decision.\n\n2. **Hotel Websites:**\n   - Visit the official websites of well-known hotel chains that might have properties in Bhopal. Examples include Taj, Marriott, Radisson, and Hyatt.\n   - Check for amenities, room types, dining options, and special services offered by these hotels.\n\n3. **Travel Review Sites:**\n   - Websites like TripAdvisor and Yelp provide user reviews and ratings that can give you insights into the experiences of other travelers.\n   - Look for hotels with high ratings and positive feedback regarding service, cleanliness, and facilities.\n\n4. **Social Media and Travel Blogs:**\n   - Follow travel bloggers and influencers who have visited Bhopal. They often share detailed reviews and recommendations.\n   - Check Instagram, X (formerly Twitter), and other social media platforms for recent posts and photos of luxury hotels in Bhopal.\n\n5. **Local Tourism Websites:**\n   - Visit the official Madhya Pradesh tourism website (or Bhopal tourism website) for a list of recommended hotels.\n   - These sites might also provide additional information about local attractions and activities.\n\n6. **Contacting Hotels Directly:**\n   - For the most accurate and up-to-date information, consider calling the hotels directly or sending an email inquiry.\n   - Ask about current rates, available packages, and any special promotions.\n\nSome well-known luxury hotels in Bhopal that you might consider are:\n\n- **Jehan Numa Palace Hotel**: Known for its historical charm and royal ambiance.\n- **Courtyard by Marriott Bhopal**: Offers modern amenities and a comfortable stay.\n- **The Oberoi Vanyavilas, Ranthambhore**: While a bit outside Bhopal, it's a luxury option for those interested in a safari experience.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to gather comprehensive information and choose the best luxury hotel for your stay in Bhopal.",
